---

<section class="bg-ink dotted-bg-dark py-32" id="cta">
  <div class="site-container">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Urgency badge -->
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red/20 text-red border border-red/30 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.15em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full mb-10">
        <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        Closing Soon &middot; Only 10 Spots
      </span>

      <!-- Heading -->
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight text-white mb-8">
        Stop losing leads.<br />
        <span class="hl-yellow-full">Build your AI.</span>
      </h2>

      <!-- Body -->
      <p class="text-white/60 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10" style="font-weight:400;">
        For the next 10 businesses we're building custom AI setters for&nbsp;<span class="bg-yellow text-ink font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md">$99</span>&nbsp;instead of up to&nbsp;<span class="line-through text-red/80">$3,797</span>. Setup, first month, and strategy call — all included.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA button -->
      <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/8x2bIUgauclZglv5Uv7bW08"
         class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-yellow text-ink font-black text-lg px-10 py-5 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-soft transition-colors mb-8">
        Yes — I Want My $99 Spot &nbsp;→
      </a>

      <!-- Trust line -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-white/60 text-sm mb-12 font-bold">
        <span>· Secure checkout</span>
        <span>· $99 goes toward your full build</span>
        <span>· Money-back guarantee on the call</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer line -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="flex-1 border-t border-white/10"></div>
        <span class="text-white/30 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.15em] whitespace-nowrap">After 10 spots, we go back to $3,797</span>
        <div class="flex-1 border-t border-white/10"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>